OL,3,CLow-cost housing will help plug public
OL,4,Csector shortage, housing lead says
OL,6,FGuernsey's new housing president wants
OL,7,Fspecial low-cost housing developments
OL,8,Fbuilt for all public sector workers to
OL,9,Fcombat "unfair" housing subsidies.
OL,11,FCurrently, workers in healthcare and
OL,12,Feducation coming from abroad are given
OL,13,Ffinancial support to help with high
OL,14,Frental costs.
OL,16,FIn some cases, that financial support
OL,17,Fcan go up to 4 years.
OL,19,FHowever, Guernsey residents are not
OL,20,Fentitled to the same such financial
OL,21,Fsupport.
