OL,3,CLow-cost housing will help plug public
OL,4,Csector shortage, housing lead says
OL,6,FDeputy Steve Williams, Guernsey's
OL,7,FPresident for Housing, describes that
OL,8,Fsystem as "unfair" for islanders.
OL,10,FHe now wants to replace the housing
OL,11,Fsubsidy with low-rent accommodation
OL,12,Ffor all public sector workers -
OL,13,Fwhether they are from home or abroad.
OL,15,FWith Guernsey facing a skills gap in
OL,16,Fthe public sector, Deputy Williams
OL,17,Fhopes this new housing could entice
OL,18,Fmore islanders to fill that shortage.
