OL,3,CLow-cost housing will help plug public
OL,4,Csector shortage, housing lead says
OL,6,FHe plans to use land owned by the
OL,7,FStates to build that low-rent
OL,8,Faccommodation.
OL,10,FIt follows concerns that only 26
OL,11,Fproperties have been built on land
OL,12,Fbought by the States of Guernsey or
OL,13,Fthe Housing Association since 2020.
OL,15,FDeputy Williams explains: "The current
OL,16,Fsystem is unfair at the moment, but I
OL,17,Fdon't think that's a controversial
OL,18,Fthing to say.
