OL,3,CLow-cost housing will help plug public
OL,4,Csector shortage, housing lead says
OL,6,F"If we were able to create key worker
OL,7,Fhousing on States-controlled land,
OL,8,Fwhich would also be for local
OL,9,Fislanders, that could be a solution."
OL,11,FDeputy Steve Williams says low-rent
OL,12,Fkey worker housing developments are
OL,13,Fbeing rolled out across the island.
OL,15,FHowever, when asked by ITV News what
OL,16,Fwill be defined as 'low-rent', Deputy
OL,17,FWilliams wasn't able to give any
OL,18,Fspecific figures.
