OL,3,CLow-cost housing will help plug public
OL,4,Csector shortage, housing lead says
OL,6,FThere is also the question of how much
OL,7,Fit will cost to build such
OL,8,Faccommodation.
OL,10,FLast week, ITV News revealed how the
OL,11,FStates spent #20 million on buying up
OL,12,Fland, with only two developments on
OL,13,Fthe 13 bought sites having been
OL,14,Fcompleted.
OL,16,FWith the Policy and Resources
OL,17,FCommittee (P&R) currently looking into
OL,18,Fthe rent review process, it is yet to
OL,19,Fbe seen what the States will decide as
OL,20,Fthe solution to the public sector
OL,21,Fshortage.
